      • intakeUntilFull

        public boolean intakeUntilFull​(double delay,
                               double power)
        intakes balls until either the hopper is full or a time delay is exceeded. this sanity checking is to ensure we don't waste time intaking forever in autonomous.
        Parameters:
        delay - the threshold for how long the intake can run, in seconds
        power - the power to run the intake at from -1 to 1
        Returns:
        false if not finished, true if finished
